title: Does this video capture a time traveler at the Battle of Mike Tyson in 1995?
subtitle: It is alleged that a viral video shows scenes using a camera phone that is not yet available to take pictures of the 1995 fight against Mike Tyson.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: It shows a video bystander travelling through time using a camera phone to take pictures at the Battle of Mike Tyson in 1995.
